### 1. Verdict
**Conditional**. 
The documentation alignment is conceptually correct and aligns with the 2026-07-08 umbrella mission (`docs/definitions/og-dolt-heresy-completion-2026-07-08.md`). However, it contains **29 broken relative markdown links** caused by moving files to `docs/archive/` but failing to update the target URLs inside the parentheses (despite updating the link text in several cases). It also contains outdated path references in code spans within `docs/README.md`. Acceptance is conditional on applying the concrete link fixes listed below.

---

